            "id": "https://ttt.td/2023/02/20/vscode-use-sshfs.html",
            "url": "https://ttt.td/2023/02/20/vscode-use-sshfs.html",
            "title": "VSCode使用SSH FS插件实现远程管理",
            "date_published": "2023-02-19T23:04:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"它是全能的\"><a href=\"#它是全能的\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"它是全能的\"></a>它是全能的</h2><div class=\"admonition info\"><p class=\"admonition-title\">我的使用场景\n</p><p>这不是博客迁到了Hexo上了嘛，由于hexo程序在我服务器上，我上网环境比较多变，之前做了VSCode的功课可以使用Remote-SSH插件实现远程管理，但是用了下发现那种ssh key登录的方式只是适合自己固定的设备上使用</p>\n<p>既要考虑便携性又要方便的话(支持密码验证)，找了一下可以使用<code>SSH FS</code>扩展</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"使用方法\"><a href=\"#使用方法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用方法\"></a>使用方法</h2><p>由于我需要使用便携版，所以我下载的portable版本的vscode</p>\n<div class=\"admonition warning\"><p class=\"admonition-title\">关于制作便携版\n</p><p>portable版本虽然是zip格式，但是解压后需要在软件目录新建data目录重新运行才能使便携版，新建data目录之后再进行打包</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>打开VSCode，进入扩展页面，快捷键<code>Ctrl+Shift+X</code></p>\n<p>搜索<code>SSH FS</code>并安装</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://input-s3.mn.input.im/adm-group/1/20230220/63f2afb4afc21.png\" alt=\"VSCode的SSH FS扩展.png\"></p>\n<p>安装之后打开扩展设置<code>config.json</code>，更改以下配置为自己的信息</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight json\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">&quot;sshfs.configs&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"punctuation\">[</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        </span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"punctuation\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"attr\">&quot;root&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;远程根目录&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"attr\">&quot;host&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;服务器IP&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"attr\">&quot;port&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"number\">22</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"attr\">&quot;username&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;root&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"attr\">&quot;password&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;密码&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"attr\">&quot;name&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;连接名称&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"attr\">&quot;merge&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"literal\"><span class=\"keyword\">true</span></span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"attr\">&quot;sftpSudo&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"literal\"><span class=\"keyword\">true</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"punctuation\">&#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// ...</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">&quot;sshfs.flags&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"punctuation\">[</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"string\">&quot;-FS_NOTIFY_ERRORS&quot;</span> <span class=\"comment\">//这个很重要，避免报build.grade错误</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"punctuation\">]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<div class=\"admonition error\"><p class=\"admonition-title\">安全建议\n</p><p>如果使用密码认证方式，不信任的设备上使用便携版需要妥善存储，例如加密打包</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>重新启动编辑器，已经可以连接<br><img src=\"https://input-s3.mn.input.im/adm-group/1/20230220/63f2b0be54c4a.png\" alt=\"连接服务器.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://input-s3.mn.input.im/adm-group/1/20230220/63f2b0ee4d548.png\" alt=\"管理服务器文件.png\"></p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "日常",
